ITEM 0 60 VAL2=1151
ITEM 1 248
;model
EXTEND 1 of the planets and sun
ITEM 2 411
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The tiny tiles are carefully fitted into mosaic images of growth and birth, flowers blooming, grapevines overrunning the arbor and animals of the field loading or nursing young. At the apex of the arch appears the image of a smiling woman whose radia
nce touches each of the other images and somehow completes them.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB TURN 1
	ECHO ALL It makes a tinkling sound.
ENDIF
;
IFPREVERB GO 0
        IFVAR ALIGN < -5
                CLEARVERB
                ECHO PLAYER You hear a voice in your mind, "Your presence is not desired here, dark one."
                ADD FLAG4 5
                DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 1 You are picked and gently put on the ground.
                EQUAL ROUNDTIME FLAG4
                ECHO OTHERS %n moves towards the door, but is picked up, stretched out prone and lowered to the street!
                POSITION LAY
        ENDIF
        IFVAR ALIGN > -4
                ECHO PLAYER You hear a gentle touch on your mind, "Welcome to my home, stay in peace and Light."
        ENDIF
        IFVAR ALIGN > -4
                IFVAR ALIGN < 1
                        ECHO PLAYER You are mildly chided "You are walking between the dark and the light.
                        ECHO PLAYER Seek to cleanse yourself in your travels ahead."
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF

