*DESCRIPTION_START
This austere room is where the clergy study the concepts of the faith,
White Necromancy, Druidic Magic, religion and other tenets that make them
what they are.  Finely paneled oak walls and lush carpet impart a luxury
that does nothing to disguise the reverence of the Lady in this room.
Various tables, shelves, and racks hold books, scrolls and tomes.
*DESCRIPTION_END
