;
Number 585
Name Knights of Shemri, Exercise Area
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
REGION 205
*DESCRIPTION_START
This long, open room is where the Knights of Shemri train for
their important task of defending the Church and upholding Shemri's
beliefs.  Various racks hold weapons, shields and other implements
of war, destroying any credence to beliefs that Shemrites are pacifists
as well.  Instructors train young knights in their trade, teaching
moves, tricks, and parries.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 1153
TRAINING 3 30
TRAINING 6 40
TRAINING 9 45
TRAINING 10 7
TRAINING 11 5
TRAINING 13 30
TRAINING 19 15
IFSAY Evaluate
        EQUAL SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL9    ; Crushing
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL13   ; Edged
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL16   ; Drakin
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL1    ; Two weapons
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL19   ; Thrown weapons
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL3    ; Missile weapons
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL4    ; Natural Weapons
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL6    ; Dodge
        MULT SHEMPRITRAIN 5
        STRCVT 0 SHEMPRITRAIN
        EQUAL SHEMSECTRAIN SKILL26 ; \
        ADD SHEMSECTRAIN SKILL27   ;  - Psionics
        ADD SHEMSECTRAIN SKILL28   ; /
        ADD SHEMSECTRAIN SKILL32   ; Sagecraft
        ADD SHEMSECTRAIN SKILL17   ; Druidic
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL20 ; healing
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL23   ; spellcraft
        ADD SHEMPRITRAIN SKILL30   ; necro
        ADD SHEMSECTRAIN SKILL10
        ADD SHEMSECTRAIN SKILL11
        MULT SHEMSECTRAIN 2
        STRCVT 1 SHEMSECTRAIN
        EQUAL SHEMTOTTRAIN SHEMPRITRAIN
        ADD SHEMTOTTRAIN SHEMSECTRAIN
        STRCVT 2 SHEMTOTTRAIN
        ECHO ALL The priestess in charge of training speaks quietly:
        ECHO ALL %N has %0 points in primary skills, %1 in secondary skills for a total of %2 %c%c
ENDIF
;
Number 588
Name Sacred Ritual Room
INDOOR_FLOOR
IFLOGIN -1
        MOVE 333
ENDIF
REGION 205
IFENTRY
        IFVAR PLRSINROOM = 1
                EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 0
        ENDIF
ENDIF
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room is almost square, and not that large, but the peace and
tranquility felt in here is beyond description.  Imbedded in the very
center of the floor is a glowing disc of the purest albescent.  The
disc is banded by concentric rings of pure white gold and white platinum.
Circling the disc about ten feet away, are a dozen majestic pillars.
Outside of the pillars, near the head of the room, is a podium on a
small two-tiered dias.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 1331
ITEM 1 1278
; ITEM 2 DIAS
ITEM 3 479
ITEM 4 81 VAL2=1152
IFPREVERB TAP 4
        STRCVT 9 INTNUM3
        GMMSG %N's INTNUM3 is %9
ENDIF
ORGDEF 10 invite cult 588 Church_of_Shemri
IFTOUCH 0
        CLEARVERB
        IFVAR ALIGN < -50
                ECHO PLAYER You feel a huge shock as pure holy wrath is vented into your helpless body.
                ECHO OTHERS You see %n being covered with intense white tendrils of light from the circle, burning and searing %h flesh.
                KILL PLAYER
        ENDIF   
        IFVAR ALIGN < -15
                IFVAR ALIGN > -51
                        DAMAGEPLR ELECTRIC 50 You feel a small surge of power, surely just a warning, flow into your body.
                        ECHO OTHERS You see %n jerk suddenly from a jolt of power as %s touches the circle.
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB BEGONE -1
        CLEARVERB
        IFVAR FLAG1 ! 0
                EQUAL FLAG1 0
                EQUAL GOSHEMPOD 0
        ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 3
        CLEARVERB
        IFVAR GOSHEMPOD = 1
                ECHO PLAYER Someone is already using the podium.
        ELSE
                ECHO PLAYER You step onto the dias and behind the podium.
                ECHO OTHERS You see %n step onto the dias and then behind the podium.
                EQUAL GOSHEMPOD 1
                EQUAL FLAG1 1
        ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR FLAG1 = 1
        IFPREVERB KICK 3
                CLEARVERB
                ECHO PLAYER You step down from the podium.
                ECHO OTHERS %N steps down from the podium.
                EQUAL FLAG1 0
                EQUAL GOSHEMPOD 0
        ELSE
                ECHO PLAYER You kick the holy podium!
                ECHO OTHERS You see %n kick the holy podium!
        ENDIF
        IFPREVERB THUMP 3
                CLEARVERB
                ECHO PLAYER You raise your hands, asking for silence.
                ECHO OTHERS %N raises %i hands, asking for silence.
        ENDIF
        IFPREVERB POKE 3
                CLEARVERB
                ADD SHEMDISCGLOW 1
                IFVAR SHEMDISCGLOW = 1
                        ECHO ALL The disc starts to glow softly with holy radiance.
                ENDIF
                IFVAR SHEMDISCGLOW = 2
                        ECHO ALL The disc grows brighter with the love of Shemri.
                ENDIF
                IFVAR SHEMDISCGLOW = 3
                        ECHO ALL The disc now emits blinding radiance, filling all with the total grace, love and power of the Earthmother.
                ENDIF
                IFVAR SHEMDISCGLOW > 3
                        EQUAL SHEMDISCGLOW 3
                        ECHO PLAYER You hear in your head the touch of Shemri 'Isn't this enough for you?'.     
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
        IFPREVERB TAP 3
                CLEARVERB
                IFVAR SHEMDISCGLOW > 0
                        SUB SHEMDISCGLOW 1
                        IFVAR SHEMDISCGLOW = 0
                                ECHO ALL The glow of the holy disc subsides to nothing, leaving you slightly wistful yet fulfilled.
                        ENDIF
                        IFVAR SHEMDISCGLOW = 1
                                ECHO ALL The brightness of the albescent disc subsides to a heart-warming glow.
                        ENDIF
                        IFVAR SHEMDISCGLOW = 2
                                ECHO ALL The nearly blinding brilliance of the manifestion of Shemri's power subsides to a loving brightness.
                        ENDIF
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
        IFSAY Initiate -1
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 399 ; Jacqueline
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Passed, Jacqueline Montagne just initiated someone in the Church of Shemri
                        ECHO ALL A new amulet sparkles into being.
                        NEWITEM 8 960 VAL5=1
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1 ; GM
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Passed, GM  just initiated someone in the Church of Shemri
                        ECHO ALL A new amulet sparkles into being.
                        NEWITEM 8 960 VAL5=1
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 5
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Passed, Cartin Greycloak  just initiated someone in the Church of Shemri
                        ECHO ALL A new amulet sparkles into being.
                        NEWITEM 8 960 VAL5=1
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 12
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Passed Thalion Grey just initiated someone in the Church of Shemri
                        ECHO ALL A new amulet sparkles into being.
                        NEWITEM 8 960 VAL5=1
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 509
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Passed Clytemnestra just initiated someone in the Church of Shemri
                        ECHO ALL A new amulet sparkles into being.
                        NEWITEM 8 960 VAL5=1
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
        IFSAY Promote
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 5
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Cartin Greycloak just promoted
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 1
                        PLREVENT 10
                        CONTPLREVENT
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 0
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 12
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Thalion Grey just promoted
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 1
                        PLREVENT 10
                        CONTPLREVENT
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 0
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 399
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Jacqueline Montagne just promoted
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 1
                        PLREVENT 10
                        CONTPLREVENT
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 0
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 509
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 Clytemnestra just promoted
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 1
                        PLREVENT 10
                        CONTPLREVENT
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 0
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 A GM just promoted
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 1
                        PLREVENT 10
                        CONTPLREVENT
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 0
                ENDIF
                IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
                        GMMSG INTNUM3 A GM just promoted
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 1
                        PLREVENT 10
                        CONTPLREVENT
                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 0
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Cleanse -1
        IFVAR FLAG1 = 1
                IFCARRY 960 145
                        IFITEM -1 WORN
                                IFVAR ITEMVAL5 > 3
                                        ECHO PLAYER You must now put a ruby on the circle.
                                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 2
                                        PLREVENT 5
                                        CONTPLREVENT
                                        EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL1 0
                                ENDIF
                        ENDIF
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB2 PUT 0
        IFVAR SHEMGLOBAL1 = 2
                IFVAR ARCHNUM = 118
                        EQUAL SHEMOFFER ITEMVAL1
                        IFVAR ITEMADJ3 = 309
                                DIV SHEMOFFER 2
                                MULT SHEMOFFER 3
                        ENDIF
                        ECHO ALL %A dissolves into a blood red mist that hovers above the surface of the circle.
                        REMOVEITEM -1
                        IFVAR SHEMOFFER > 50000
                                ECHO ALL A melodic voice speaks "The offering is sufficient to power the ritual, would the afflicted one touch the circle."
                                EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL2 1
                                PLREVENT 3
                                CONTPLREVENT
                                EQUAL SHEMGLOBAL2 0
                        ELSE
                                ECHO ALL A melodic voice speaks "The offering is not sufficient to power the ritual."
                        ENDIF
                ELSE
                        ECHO ALL A melodic voice speaks "This is not a ruby."
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR SHEMGLOBAL2 = 1
        IFPREVERB TOUCH 0
                IFVAR INTNUM57 ! 0
                        ECHO ALL Yes, this one is afflicted, allow me to help %i.
                        DIV SHEMOFFER 1000
                        SUB INTNUM98 SHEMOFFER
                        ECHO PLAYER Your body is racked with white light, at once soothing and painful both.
                        PLREVENT 3
                        CONTPLREVENT
                        DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 300 After a violent explosion of light, pain and love, your body collapses, spent, on the circle.
                        POSITION LAY
                        IFVAR INTNUM98 < 1
                                EQUAL INTNUM98 0
                                EQUAL INTNUM57 0
                                ECHO ALL A melodic voice speaks "The victim is totally cured."
                        ELSE
                                ECHO ALL A melodic voice speaks "The victim has only been partially cured."
                        ENDIF
                ELSE
                        ECHO ALL A melodic voice speaks "The person is not afflicted with the curse."
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB2 PUT 0
        IFVAR ARCHNUM = 960
                IFVAR SHEMGLOBAL1 = 1
                        GMMSG %n in the Church of Shemri.
                        ADD ITEMVAL5 1
                        ECHO ALL The pin sparkles with the blessing of Shemri.
                ENDIF
                IFVAR SHEMGLOBAL1 = 0
                        GMMSG %N is too slow... or else they're just trying it without aid in the Church of Shemri.
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF
